<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-37-0592 </DOCNO><TEXT>The article concentrates on the economics of the breeder reactor technology.The author explains why there is no chance of an economically efficientoperation of a fast breeder reactor in the foreseeable future. Judgingfrom the economic point of view, there is no reason at all to continuespending public funds for this technological programme.</TEXT></DOC>